16('Ocular System', 'The system responsible for vision and processing visual information.', 'Enables vision by processing light and transmitting visual signals to the brain.', 'Eyes, Retina, Optic Nerve', 'Cataracts, Glaucoma, Macular Degeneration', 'Third Eye', 'Ether', true, 15),
